            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E8%AF%A5%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%B2%BB%E7%96%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E8%AF%A5%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%B2%BB%E7%96%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#感染甲流病毒该如何治疗#</span></a>【关于甲流病毒，这些要点你要知道！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[感冒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ganmao-286fc59b6d.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E8%A6%81%E7%82%B9%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E8%A6%81%E7%82%B9%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#这些甲流病毒要点要知道#</span></a>近日，全国多地部分学校因学生发热而停课，发热原因主要为甲型流感。什么是甲流？甲流有哪些症状？学校和托幼机构如何预防流感？一旦感染，该如何治疗一起学习👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4874858958618752" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">新华网的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/0034c2ttly1hbliz82i0pj61hc0u076s02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/f5y5OMkxlx083ynXk7U401041200AapG0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1A1eh1m4ElLYfp&amp;Expires=1677788349&amp;ssig=Ol7SISap55&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/4yaZTzgMlx083ynWD58c01041200ivjc0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1A1eh1m4ElLYfp&amp;Expires=1677788349&amp;ssig=v5Mnp9kuQa&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video