            <title><![CDATA[【#一招自测脱发程度#[吃惊]】国家卫健委数据显示，中国脱发患者约2.5亿人，#我国每6个人中就有1个人脱发#。如何判断自己是否脱发？专家推荐“拉发测试法”，用3...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%80%E6%8B%9B%E8%87%AA%E6%B5%8B%E8%84%B1%E5%8F%91%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%80%E6%8B%9B%E8%87%AA%E6%B5%8B%E8%84%B1%E5%8F%91%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%A6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#一招自测脱发程度#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】国家卫健委数据显示，中国脱发患者约2.5亿人，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E6%AF%8F6%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%891%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%B1%E5%8F%91%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E6%AF%8F6%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%891%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%B1%E5%8F%91%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我国每6个人中就有1个人脱发#</span></a>。如何判断自己是否脱发？专家推荐“拉发测试法”，用3个手指在不同的区域抓取50~60根头发，如果每次拉下来的头发超过6根，就可能存在脱发问题。此外，还有中分发缝测试法、压发测试法、辫子测试法等。你的脱发程度怎么样？一起测测👇🏻 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4874233407537192" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视一套的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/78ad4dbbly1hbjkmab300j21hc0u00vh.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/cDCS3zmWlx083vGszXzi01041200OPjD0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677788365&amp;ssig=nziImFjhS6&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/3L1CoJTFlx083vGrSknm01041200qhoU0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677788365&amp;ssig=OkU%2BV4LPpZ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/lX7NnW5Nlx083vGs0cbK01041200hbPU0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677788365&amp;ssig=ZbGzwWAfBn&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4874233407537192&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
